              <span id="reviewTextContainer61948920" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6176592529049618562">Finished it in three days. God, I love Fforde. His infallible main characters do get on my nerves at times, but I&apos;m not exactly in these series for their earthshattering complexities &amp; characterisations -- I&apos;m in it for bizarre plot twists, literary humour, and wacky feel-good endings, which he always delivers in spades.</span>
  <span id="freeText6176592529049618562" style="display:none">Finished it in three days. God, I love Fforde. His infallible main characters do get on my nerves at times, but I'm not exactly in these series for their earthshattering complexities &amp; characterisations -- I'm in it for bizarre plot twists, literary humour, and wacky feel-good endings, which he always delivers in spades.</span>
