        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2698341646" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3998261132490017423">I wish there was more of this series! Some good witty lines and the narrator, Simon Vance, did an excellent job bringing the colorful variety of nursery rhyme characters to life.</span>

          </span>
